oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Riders at Little Cove
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two boys, of Little Cove, horseback riding on a Sunday down a dirt road, surrounded by trees and foliage. Both horses are dark, one boy wears a hat and button down, the other is in overalls.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
